  "title": "TerrariaCraft 🌳",
  "description": "Adding Terraria content to Minecraft.",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://terrariacraft.com/\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://github.com/terrariacraft/News/blob/master/media/logo3.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" width=\"622\" height=\"150\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://discord.terrariacraft.com/\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #00ccff; font-size: 24px; text-decoration: underline;\">DISCORD</span></strong></span></a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"js-qwynlraxz\" href=\"https://discord.terrariacraft.com\"><img src=\"https://ds.zeith.org/cards/tc.png\" width=\"510\" height=\"170\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>This mod adds content from Terraria.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>The <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>plan</strong></span> is to add 95+% of all Terraria content to Minecraft. Our team is working on it.</h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://terrariacraft.com/\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">Also make sure to check out our website, we have a custom launcher for early access builds!</span></a></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #800000; font-size: 36px;\">Disclaimer:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #800000; font-size: 36px;\">This mod is a standalone project that is NOT&nbsp;intended to be used as a part of a modpack. Only addons are supported.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #800000; font-size: 36px;\">OptiFine? NO.&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 8px;\">Unless cubic chunks will support it in the future.</span></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px;\">This mod is NOT supported for android/ios emulated Minecraft: Java&nbsp; Edition, do not ask for support.</span></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px;\">This mod has troubles working on dedicated servers and generally is NOT intended to work with it.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"color: #800000; font-size: 24px;\">IF YOU ARE A YOUTUBER WILLING TO RECORD A SHOWCASE (10k+ subscribers), ASK US ON OUR DISCORD TO PROVIDE YOU EARLY ACCESS</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">NOTE:</span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><b>This mod requires </b></span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #00ffff;\"><b><a class=\"js-qwynlraxz\" style=\"color: #00ffff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/4Y5irTB9\"><img src=\"https://curseforge.zeith.org/api/v2/logo?id=289079\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Music Layer 12.2.22+</a></b></span><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><b> to work!</b></span></strong></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><b>This mod requires </b></span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #00ffff;\"><b><a class=\"js-qwynlraxz\" style=\"color: #00ffff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/PlkSuVtM\"><img src=\"https://curseforge.zeith.org/api/v2/logo?id=247401\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;HammerLib 12.2.49+</a></b></span><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><b> to work!</b></span></strong></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><b>This mod requires </b></span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #00ffff;\"><b><a class=\"js-qwynlraxz\" style=\"color: #00ffff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/C7cTlgwS\"><img src=\"https://curseforge.zeith.org/api/v2/logo?id=899883\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;HammerAnimations 12.2.21+</a></b></span><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><b> to work!</b></span></strong></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><b>This mod requires </b></span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #00ffff;\"><b><a class=\"js-qwynlraxz\" style=\"color: #00ffff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/8Tb4j8xo\"><img src=\"https://curseforge.zeith.org/api/v2/logo?id=292243\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;OpenCubicChunks 0.0.1055+</a></b></span><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><b> to work!</b></span></strong></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><b>This mod is compatible with </b></span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #00ffff;\"><b><a class=\"js-qwynlraxz\" style=\"color: #00ffff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/WbZWY2NM\"><img src=\"https://curseforge.zeith.org/api/v2/logo?id=341357\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Corsair McCUE 12.4.10</a></b></span><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><b>!</b></span></strong></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><b>This mod looks a lot better with </b></span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #00ffff;\"><b><a class=\"js-qwynlraxz\" style=\"color: #00ffff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/mEr4VarV\"><img src=\"https://curseforge.zeith.org/api/v2/logo?id=347912\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;ColoredLux 12.6.33+</a></b></span><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><b> to work!</b></span></strong></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Configs are located at .minecraft/terraria/ModConfigs.cfg</strong></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Some images:</p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/GbY79zK.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NKNTxcN.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aYpvs2k.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8py6ARh.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6bj8LVF.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bM7i2yw.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uceyTfD.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/v60FBPr.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/shdOCIA.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8fy0BpD.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bNoKKYU.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4sGoJfG.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3qstYfM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ENk952p.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pkrU06y.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DWefkt1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">If you want to get content earlier, feel free to subscribe to our Patreon!</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">You also need a paid Minecraft account, and you have to be on our Terraria Craft discord server.</span></p>\n<p><a class=\"js-qwynlraxz\" href=\"https://www.patreon.com/join/zeitheron/checkout?rid=3054296\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mrak7w3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"460\" height=\"200\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LuJJMv1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"698\" height=\"1\" /></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Permissions:</strong></p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>You&nbsp;can use this mod in your modpack.</strong></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>You are not allowed to re-publish this mod to other sites without providing a Modrinth/CurseForge download link and my permission (PM to <img src=\"https://assets.zeith.org/icons/zeitheron.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />&nbsp;Zeitheron via Discord)</strong></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>You are not allowed to include this (or any other mods of the DragonForge team) in your own mod. Building add-ons, however, is allowed, but a friendly PM would be good.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>The only supported version of Minecraft is the latest one that this mod exists for. DO NOT ASK TO DOWNGRADE!</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"js-qwynlraxz\" href=\"https://ds.zeith.org/dev\"><img src=\"https://ds.zeith.org/cards/dev.png\" width=\"510\" height=\"170\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Or you can join our specialized server: (development progress, community, and feedback)</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"js-qwynlraxz\" href=\"https://discord.terrariacraft.com\"><img src=\"https://ds.zeith.org/cards/tc.png\" width=\"510\" height=\"170\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Want to discuss anything? Need help with APIs?</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Join the discord server and follow Zeitheron on <a class=\"js-qwynlraxz\" href=\"http://bit.ly/ZeithTwitter\"><img src=\"https://abs.twimg.com/favicons/twitter.ico\" alt=\"\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" />Twitter</a>!</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>If you would like to support my work, you can become a patron via <a class=\"js-qwynlraxz\" href=\"https://www.patreon.com/zeitheron\"><img src=\"https://c5.patreon.com/external/favicon/favicon-32x32.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" />&nbsp;Patreon</a>.</strong></p>",
